{
 "name": "RPlog_Raxis_Gets_Shot_Down",
 "title": "Raxis Gets Shot Down",
 "summary": "Over the contested border world of Bimmissari, the New Republic pilot Raxis leads a Ranger reconnaissance patrol that runs headlong into an Imperial trap. The Imperial ace Krieg and his Raptor flight, supported by the Star Destroyer Nemesis, ambush the Republic craft, and Raxis's X-Wing is shredded and sent crashing planetside, forcing him to bail out with his astromech. As Krieg's pilots, including Dante, methodically destroy the recon Y-Wings, the surviving Republic fighters -- Rebecca's Ghost Nine and the shuttle pilot Askra -- fight to cover the retreat and escape to hyperspace. Stranded and dirt-covered on the surface, a disbelieving Raxis watches the Imperial shuttle that hunted him simply depart, leaving him alive amid the wreckage.",
